{"tid":2326113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我認為連登仔要面對大紀元真係變美國官方喉舌既現實","createTime":"2020-12-15T05:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:02:37.000Z","uid":58841,"like":62,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"76fd421566046d5b05a27ffde91977f7ecdeb238","tid":2326113,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"大紀元報支那野可以當fake<br />\n但係連登仔係咪忘恩負義到唔記得左大紀元係反送中做過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國遊行直播其實我有睇開<br />\n因為以我經驗現實同媒體報好多時候有落差<br />\n對上幾次大紀元想做訪問個陣個個美國人反應係No thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係上一次遊行已經係大紀元多到做唔切訪問<br />\n個個衝埋去講I&rsquo;d like to talk something<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n演講好多都讚緊大紀元報真野<br />\n而英文大紀元app排名已經係全美媒體類頭幾名<br />\n連侵都retweet埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢目前假假地都係個總統黎既<br />\n唔知連登仔仲覺唔覺得大紀元係fake news傳媒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821cf0e410743fa544e5290062cdb88f6a61951c","tid":2326113,"uid":70487,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SidneyPowell1/status/1338370112810782725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSidneyPowell1%2Fstatus%2F1338370112810782725&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGJwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=8086b415\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSidneyPowell1%2Fstatus%2F1338370112810782725&h=11410fbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SidneyPowell1/status/1338370112810782725</a>"},{"pid":"fa4979b264fdf6f60ce16459ef5cb709d1085d53","tid":2326113,"uid":58841,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"821cf0e410743fa544e5290062cdb88f6a61951c","tid":2326113,"uid":70487,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,